snippet.title: Best VGM 1485 - Paper Mario : Sticker Star - Snow Rise
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

3DS
Paper Mario : Sticker Star (2012)
Snow Rise
Saki Kurata, Shoh Murakami, Yoshito Sakigawa, Yasuhisa Baba, Hiroki Morishita, Masanori Adachi, Kiyoshi Hazemoto, Tomoko Sano, Kosei Muraki, Hiroaki Hanaoka & Yasumasa Yamada
